body:
Sup, so recently I have been noticing some people have FPS issues, or that some people just want better fps in general. Either people are on lowend laptops (like yours truly) and have no idea how to better optimise their FPS or people with actually pretty good set up don't know how to get the most out of their mineman experience. So with this said, I will put screenshots of the best video settings that I personally use so hopefully you guys can use them as well.

NOTE: Some of these settings you may or may not like, but for me they work. Some people like playing with particles on max or with view bobbing or above 2 render distance and that's fine, but as long as you follow most of these settings you'll get better fps :)

Screenshots of my settings:
When you first open Video Settings: https://i.gyazo.com/6e539e38cb8d757de5ddd4938a5bd213.png
Details: https://gyazo.com/5a29ed260a8486e3732493edbcf79ab6
Animations (you can have this as you like, as long as particles are on decreased. having it like this makes it so you see crit particles or walking particles for invis kiddies): https://gyazo.com/05320321ea1d88b96a11351716466ff8
Quality: https://gyazo.com/fc177f8fe806b785dadb2b441650549b
Performance: https://gyazo.com/1eee93682803085ac9ec10eccece996f
Other (as well as how to turn off rain or snow): https://gyazo.com/2deca94ab6350eb6c950e3012b864ead

Along with changing video settings, you can edit your windows settings to optimise fps. You do this by going to the taskbar in the bottom left and...
1) search "performance"
2) clicking on "adjust the performance and appearance of windows"
3) click on the option saying "adjust for best performance" and then scroll down and click on "show thumbnails instead of icons" 

Extras:
After all this, you should have gotten the most out of your fps, but to squeeze just a little more I have also included below my 8x Celestial FPS pack and my mods folder (you only really need the sidebarmod and fastchat by Fyu for the fps, but the rest is just for lols) 
Mods: http://www.mediafire.com/file/5fbgn2yg6r3y23n/mods_for_1.8.9.zip
*how fast chat works - takes away the black box behind chat, looks nicer + increases fps?*
*how sidebarmod works - gives you the option to take away the scoreboard on the side of your screen*
FPS Pack: http://www.mediafire.com/file/i9mjg8z12mf1wl3/Celestial_FPS.zip (pictures below)
